2. Keyword Research and Selection
Keyword research is a critical component of Google Ads success. PPC agencies conduct in-depth keyword research to identify relevant keywords with high search volume and low competition. By targeting the right keywords, businesses can attract qualified traffic and increase their chances of conversion.
