4. Bid Management and Budget Optimization
Effective bid management is crucial for achieving optimal ad placement and maximizing budget efficiency. PPC agencies monitor bidding strategies, adjust bid amounts based on performance data, and optimize budget allocation to ensure maximum return on investment.
