Tracking and analyzing campaign performance metrics is essential for evaluating the effectiveness of Google Ads campaigns. PPC agencies provide detailed performance reports, including metrics such as click-through rate (CTR), conversion rate, cost-per-click (CPC), and return on ad spend (ROAS), enabling businesses to make informed decisions and optimize campaign strategies.
